<seg id="13"> For the People's Congress to do a good job in the new situation, the first thing should be to stick to a correct political direction, firmly walk on the developmental path of socialist politics with Chinese features, and organically integrate staying with the leadership of the Party, people being in charge, and governing the country according to laws. </seg>
<seg id="14"> The second thing should be to focus on the major work of the party and state, important issues in reforms and developments, and working on hot and difficult issues that the masses of people care about, and continuously strengthen the efficiency of the work of the People's Congress. </seg>
