</p>
<p>
<seg id="2"> GUIYANG, February 16 (Xinhua)(Reporter: Shi Xinrong) On the afternoon of the 16th, adults and children in Tianlong Village, Tianlong Township, Pingba County in the province of Guizhou were putting on their fine festival clothing. Their faces wore smiles brimming with happiness. </seg>
