<seg id="3"> That is, Tsuneo Watanabe, chairman of one of Japan's leading papers, the Yomiuri Shimbun, he ordered Yomiuri Shimbun to publish some articles ...eh ... that oppose Koizumi's visit to the Yasukuni Shrine, marking Yomiuri Shimbun's shift to a stand against Koizumi's visit to Yasukuni Shrine. </seg>
